      "content": "That's a bit vague. Can you get more specific with the actual types of sentences? For Case A, would you lean more towards probation or community service because of his background? And for Case B, would the \"urban background\" and employment instability actually make a judge more likely to push for actual jail time instead of just rehabilitation?",
